Redistributed Data Sources
--------------------------

This project redistributes unmodified data from third-party sources under the Creative Commons Attribution-Share Alike 4.0 International (CC BY-SA 4.0) license.

**KanjiDic2 and KanjiDict XML datasets**  

    - Source: Electronic Dictionary Research and Development Group (EDRDG)  
    - License: CC BY-SA 4.0 (upgraded from 3.0)  
    - Website: https://www.edrdg.org/wiki/index.php/KANJIDIC_Project  
    - Includes: kanjidic2.xml.gz and related files

**KanjiVG stroke order graphics**  

    - Source: Ulrich Apel  
    - License: CC BY-SA 4.0 (upgraded from 3.0)  
    - Website: https://kanjivg.tagaini.net/  
    - Includes: SVG files modeling kanji character strokes

These datasets are redistributed **verbatim and unmodified**. All copyright and licensing obligations remain with the original authors.
By using this software or accessing redistributed data, you agree to comply with the CC BY-SA 4.0 license.

For full license terms, visit: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

